
"Yeah that would help my back a lot, thanks." he says as he climbs in while I scoot over.
He turns his bed side lamp off and comes closer to me, wrapping his arm around my waist and holding me close. I feel safe in his arms and I turn and face him, looking into his glowing blue eyes and smile, feeling sleep wash over me like a tsunami. He pushes a piece of my hair behind my ear and whispers barely audible as I drift into sleep.
Goodnight beautiful.
